DESCRIPTION:Grab your bike and come on our to our second-annual Chavis Bike
  Rodeo! We'll have a pop-up traffic garden to explore a miniature world of 
 streets\, a series of skill stations\, and a bike obstacle course. Bikes an
 d helmets will be available to borrow. This event is in partnership with Wa
 ke County Safe Routes to School and Chavis Park.<br><br>Organizer/community
  partner: Oaks &amp\; Spokes and Wake County Safe Routes to School<br><ul><
 li><b>Passport eligible? </b>Yes</li><li><b>Registration required?</b> No</
 li></ul>
