UID:4vtj5roamjuf7qe4q677og0qcl@google.com
CREATED:20260403T155811Z
DESCRIPTION:Help NC Families for Safe Streets advocate for Intelligent Spee
 d Assist technology that would reduce deaths caused by "super speeders".<br
 ><ul><li>Attendees Arrive by 9:30 am</li><li>Press Conference Begins  - 10 
 am </li><li>We will hold a press conference featuring the stories FSS membe
 rs\, coalition partners\, and community leaders urging the need for this le
 gislation.</li><li>ISA Tech Demonstration - TBD There will be a live demons
 tration of the intelligent speed assistance technology. Legislators\, the p
 ress\, legislative staff\, and others will be able to test drive a vehicle 
 equipped with ISA.</li><li>Lobby Visits - TBD</li></ul><br>Throughout the d
 ay\, participants will meet directly with elected officials—both before and
  after the press event—to urge passage of a Stop Super Speeders bill that w
 ill protect all North Carolinians. These meetings are a powerful opportunit
 y to share stories\, present data\, and make clear that safer streets are a
  priority across our communities. Want to share your story or lobby? Regist
 er <a href="https://secure.everyaction.com/vFvg9xltZ0mQ2ps7dithAw2" target=
 "_blank">here</a>.<br><br>Organizer/community partner: NC Families for Safe
  Streets<ul><li><b>Passport eligible?</b> No</li><li><b>Registration requir
 ed?</b> <a href="https://secure.everyaction.com/vFvg9xltZ0mQ2ps7dithAw2" ta
 rget="_blank">Yes</a> (for lobbying/speaking)</li></ul>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T160234Z
LOCATION:North Carolina State Capitol\, 1 E Edenton St\, Raleigh\, NC 27601
 \, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Stop Super Speeders Lobby Day
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
